  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will provide efficacy data for Creon 25000 MMS in PS patients as well as long-term
      safety data. During the long-term treatment with Creon 25000 nutritional parameters will be
      assessed and correlated with CFA
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
